JSON record parser implementation.

    A RecordReader implementation for JSON formatted records.

    A RecordMarshaller implementation for JSON formatted records.
    JsonRecordParserFactory
    A RecordParserFactory for JSON formatted streams.
    JsonRecordUnmarshaller
    A RecordUnmarshaller implementation for JSON formatted records.
    JsonWriter
    A RecordWriter implementation for writing JSON formatted record.
    JsonWriterSupport
    Base class for writing a JSON formatted stream.
